::::: green
::: green-ttl
Confidence interval for $\mu_1 - \mu_2$
:::

::: green-cont
$$\overline{x}_1 - \overline{x}_2 \pm\ t^*\times \text{SE}$$

-   with $\text{SE} = \sqrt{\frac{s_{1}^2}{n_{1}}+\frac{s_{2}^2}{n_2}}$ if population sd is not known
:::
